    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: clueDialogueLines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: solvedConversation.Array.size
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: initialConversation.Array.size
      value: 6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: clueDialogueLines.Array.data[0].text
      value: Hey, I was just looking at the whiteboard earlier. Some of those scribbles
        might actually be related to what you're working on.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: solvedConversation.Array.data[0].text
      value: So how did it go, Detective? Are we now certain that the machine is
        right?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: solvedConversation.Array.data[1].text
      value: Please Detective, I recomputed everything! I just learned about percentages
        in my math class recently, and I know I'm right!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: solvedConversation.Array.data[2].text
      value: Ms. Cafeteria Lady, how much exactly did you give this little kid?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: solvedConversation.Array.data[3].text
      value: Hmm, I gave her
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: initialConversation.Array.data[0].text
      value: 'Hi. I heard the Science Fair experiment is missing.

        Do you
        know what happened?'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: initialConversation.Array.data[1].text
      value: "We don\u2019t know\u2026\nWe were just practicing here."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: initialConversation.Array.data[2].text
      value: Practicing what?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: initialConversation.Array.data[3].text
      value: We were practicing using ice. We left our practice setup on the table
        to grab some supplies.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: initialConversation.Array.data[4].text
      value: And when you came back?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: initialConversation.Array.data[5].text
      value: The experiment was missing.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: clueDialogueLines.Array.data[0].speakerName
      value: Ben
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2684024005323760421, guid: 137d9f1a140044e4f9c3481cc59776ef,
